+    // accumulate-reduce → ŵ_i). Constraints VERBATIM from expanda_matvec_air.rs; only the counts
+    // shrink (l=1, N=64, C=320 kept). Exposes pi_stream (320 packs) + ẑ/t̂1/ĉ (64 each) as INPUT
+    // publics and the REAL ŵ_i[0..64] as OUTPUT publics. The placed Â feeds the mult b-input
